        <updateDate>2025-04-28T15:11:47Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fair Funding for Rural Hospitals Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill establishes a minimum funding allotment for Medicaid disproportionate-share hospitals (DSHs). (DSHs are hospitals that receive additional payments under Medicaid for treating a large share of low-income patients.)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Specifically, the bill establishes a minimum allotment of $20 million per state for FY2025-FY2029, increased for inflation in subsequent years, despite any required reductions or other applicable funding calculations.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
